<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>전체 접수 목록 - MediCare+</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
  <script src="/js/feather.min.js"></script>
</head>
<body>
  {{> common/sidebar-admin}}

  <div class="main-content flex-1 flex flex-col ml-64">
    {{> common/header-staff}}

    <main class="content-wrapper">
      <div class="space-y-6 max-w-6xl mx-auto">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-8">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-indigo-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-indigo-600">
            <i data-feather="clipboard" class="w-6 h-6"></i>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h1 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-800">전체 접수 목록</h1>
            <p class="text-slate-500 mt-1">데이터 로직은 2차 작업에서 연결됩니다.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-slate-200 p-6">
          <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm">현재는 화면 연결 상태만 제공합니다. (placeholder)</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </main>

    {{> common/footer-staff}}
  </div>

  <script>
    if (typeof feather !== 'undefined') {
      feather.replace();
    }
  </script>
</body>
</html>

